com.inqwell.any.beans

Class PropertySet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inqwell.any.AbstractAny
      • com.inqwell.any.beans.PropertySet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Any, Serializable

    public class PropertySet
extends AbstractAny
    This class when given a java bean will allow easy access to various property bean info. At present, only write access to an object's properties is supported.
